config BR2_PACKAGE_ADOS_RKMPI_WRAPPER
    bool "ados-rkmpi-wrapper"
    depends on BR2_arm
    depends on BR2_TOOLCHAIN_USES_UCLIBC
    help
      Subprocess wrapper that bridges the lite Rust agent to the
      Rockchip RKMPI hardware H.264 / H.265 encoder on RV1106 / RV1106G3
      (Luckfox Pico Zero). Built against the closed-source Luckfox SDK;
      requires SDK_ROOT to point at a Luckfox SDK clone.

      Without this package, the Rust agent's video pipeline silently
      disables on Luckfox boards.
